(41, 7, 37, 19, 139, 14, 14, NULL, 'Connection of Divine Creation and Healing', 'Both passages emphasize the marvelous works of God. Mark 7:37 highlights the healing of the deaf and dumb, while Psalms 139:14 praises the wonder of human creation.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
